---
import { getLang } from "../lib/i18n";
const lang = getLang(Astro.url);
const isEn = lang === "en";

const t = {
  sectionId: isEn ? "about" : "nosotros",
  imgAlt: isEn
    ? "Pastor preaching in a school during a LUZ Impacto event"
    : "Pastor predicando en un colegio durante un evento de LUZ Impacto",
  eyebrow: isEn ? "Who we are" : "Quiénes somos",
  cta: isEn ? "See what we do" : "Conocer qué hacemos",
  ctaHref: isEn ? "#what-we-do" : "#que-hacemos",
};
---

<section class="section" id={t.sectionId}>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="/assets/photos/about.jpg" alt={t.imgAlt} loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <div class="eyebrow">{t.eyebrow}</div>
        {isEn ? (
          <>
            <h2>A bridge between youth and the church.</h2>
            <p class="stat-line">
              In Costa Rica, thousands of young people spend <strong>11 years in school</strong> without ever hearing the gospel.
            </p>
            <p>
              That's what LUZ came to change. We're a Costa Rican evangelical Christian ministry founded in 2024. <strong>We're not a church</strong> — we're a bridge.
            </p>
            <p>
              We go to schools across the country preaching the message of salvation. When a young person receives Christ, we connect them with partner churches in their area that can disciple them and walk with them in their new life.
            </p>
            <div class="quote-block">
              "You are the light of the world. A town built on a hill cannot be hidden."
              <div class="cite">— MATTHEW 5:14</div>
            </div>
          </>
        ) : (
          <>
            <h2>Un puente entre los jóvenes y las iglesias.</h2>
            <p class="stat-line">
              En Costa Rica, miles de jóvenes pasan <strong>11 años en colegios</strong> sin escuchar nunca el evangelio.
            </p>
            <p>
              Eso es lo que LUZ vino a cambiar. Somos un ministerio cristiano evangélico costarricense fundado en 2024. <strong>No somos una iglesia</strong> — somos un puente.
            </p>
            <p>
              Vamos a colegios de todo el país predicando el mensaje de salvación. Cuando un joven recibe a Cristo, lo conectamos con iglesias locales aliadas que lo pueden discipular y acompañar en su nueva vida.
            </p>
            <div class="quote-block">
              "Vosotros sois la luz del mundo; una ciudad asentada sobre un monte no se puede esconder."
              <div class="cite">— MATEO 5:14</div>
            </div>
          </>
        )}
        <a href={t.ctaHref} class="btn btn-ghost-dark">{t.cta} <span class="arrow">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .about-image {
    border-radius: 20px;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }
  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 6%;
    display: block;
  }
  .about-text h2 { margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .about-text p { font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .about-text .stat-line {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .about-text .stat-line strong {
    color: var(--charcoal);
    border-bottom: 3px solid var(--yellow);
  }
  .about-text p:last-of-type { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .quote-block {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--yellow);
    padding: 12px 0 12px 24px;
    margin: 32px 0;
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .cite {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    margin-top: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
    .about-image { aspect-ratio: 4/3; }
  }
</style>
